EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO PUBLIC UTILITIES AND CARRIERS -- REGULATORY POWERS OF
ADMINISTRATION
***
1 This act would require a natural gas and electric utility company to read the meters of all
2 ratepayers on a quarterly basis. The utility would be required to provide a formula, used to create
3 estimated bills, to the PUC in order to send estimated bills.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
